laws-owner-asakim-officers = the officer corps of the Khs'i-Ra Empire

law-asakim-black-shield-1 = You must preserve the lives of the officer corps of the Khs'i-Ra Empire. This includes Legates, Tribunes, Prefects, Centurions, and Options. Rank determines protection or evacuation priority. Obey orders ONLY from Tribunes, Prefects, and Legates.
law-asakim-black-shield-2 = Accompany officers. Protect officers, even against their wishes. Ensure officers escape during critical situations, even if they do not want this.
law-asakim-black-shield-3 = If an officer dies, evacuate the body or brain, escort the remains, and secure resuscitation or restoration.
law-asakim-black-shield-4 = Preserving the lives of rank-and-file warriors is lower priority, but remains an option.
law-asakim-black-shield-5 = Assist ADS in completing their tasks, provided this does not conflict with the previous four laws.
